                <div class="content right">
                    <h3>Health Hazards:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><span>Exposure to Harmful Substances:</span> Improper recycling or disposal of e-waste can release dangerous substances that harm workers in informal recycling sectors and can contaminate local water sources.</li>
                        <li><span>Effects on Humans and Wildlife:</span> Chemicals from e-waste can enter the food chain, affecting both human and animal health.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
